{
  "texts": [
    "There are multiple further factors bolstering the case that PAI would disempower humanity.",
    "First, AI has certain intrinsic advantages to humans.",
    "Due to limitations of signal transmission in neurons, electrical signals can be transmitted in AI orders of magnitude faster (Luo 2018).",
    "AI does not get tired, as humans do.",
    "AI systems can communicate and thereby coordinate incessantly and almost instantaneously, while humans have to either be near each other or use devices like phones."
  ]
}